data.description:
Welcome to 210 Lorita Way, Hanford, CA 93230 - a beautifully remodeled residence in the heart of Hanford's historic district. This 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home has undergone a thoughtful transformation, featuring 1328 square feet of living space on a spacious 8970 square feet lot. Recent updates include new paint that brings a fresh and modern feel to the interior. The addition of can lights enhances the ambiance, providing a well-lit and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen has been tastefully upgraded with new countertops, a stylish backsplash, and new flooring, offering a seamless blend of functionality and contemporary design.


Step outside into the beautifully landscaped yard, where the backyard becomes a true oasis. A delightful pool invites you to relax, and a versatile workshop offers space for DIY projects or extra storage. The covered porch is perfect for outdoor gatherings, and the in-ground fire pit adds a cozy and inviting element, creating the perfect setting for memorable evenings under the stars.

An exciting feature of this home is an extra, unused room that awaits the buyer's creative touch. Whether it becomes an additional bedroom, home office, or a personalized space, the potential is endless for customization to suit your lifestyle.


Situated near Hanford High School, this remodeled home is nestled in an older and historic area, adding character and charm to your everyday life. The blend of a peaceful residential setting with the convenience of nearby amenities makes 210 Lorita Way a unique opportunity to embrace the distinctive charm of Hanford living. Don't miss out on making this residence with a perfect blend of of modern updates, original features, and customizable space.
